50|$|Solidaridad {{launched}} a {{multi-annual strategic plan}} in 2016 which defined new result areas for development: good practices, robust infrastructures, landscape innovations, and enabling policy environments. These four result areas contribute to two overarching aims: sustainable and inclusive sectors, and sustainable landscapes. <b>Good</b> <b>agricultural</b> <b>practices</b> remain a focus point for Solidaridad's work.|$|R
